casebody.data:
Billy ROWE and Robin Rowe, Plaintiffs-Appellees/ Cross-Appellants,
v.
Detective/sergeant Ronald AINSLIE, Defendant, Cross-Appellee,
and
Trooper Steve Lamb, Defendant,
and
Trooper Dennis Milburn, Defendant-Appellant/ Cross-Appellee. SC: 155709
COA: 332566 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's November 16, 2017 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
